FBIS4-59427 "drnes093_l_94007" FBIS-NES-94-093 Daily Report 12 May 1994 ISRAEL `Terrorists' Caught `Terrorists' Caught TA1205132094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1300 GMT 12 May 94 TA1205132094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Excerpt] IDF [Israel Defense Forces] soldiers in the Gaza Strip apprehended the terrorists who wounded an Israeli truck driver near the settlement of Morag today. Our correspondent Nisim Qeynan reports that the terrorists overtook the truck and opened fire. The driver, who was wounded in the chest and leg, was transferred to Soroka Hospital. Following the incident, IDF forces sealed off the area, launched a manhunt, and caught the terrorists. [passage omitted]
